'''''Battles of Napoleon''''' is a 1988 [[computer wargame]] by [[Chuck Kroegel]] and David Landrey published by [[Strategic Simulations]]. It was released for the [[Apple II series|Apple II]], [[Commodore 64]], and [[DOS]].

